How to release
==============

* Update CHANGELOG
* Update version in docs/source/conf.py
* Update the file info.py
* Add label: git tag -a vx.y -m 'my version x.y'
* Create a tarball and upload it on github
    git archive master | bzip2 > vitalus-x.y.tar.bz2
* Send the package on pypi
    python setup.py sdist upload
